<exploration xml:id="warm-cuantosVes-tablerosDe5YDedos" xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude"> 

<title>Cuántos ves: Tableros de 5 y dedos</title>

<statement>
  <line>¿Cuántos ves?</line>
  <line>¿Cómo lo sabes?, ¿qué ves?</line>
  <image source="svg-source/tikz-file-141786">
    <shortdescription>5 puntos.</shortdescription>
  </image>
  <image source="svg-source/tikz-file-141787">
    <shortdescription>6 puntos.</shortdescription>
  </image>
  <image source="png-source/hand 6b.png" width="25%">
    <shortdescription>6 dedos.</shortdescription>
  </image>
</statement>

<solution>
    <p>[+++++++++++++++]</p>
    <p>Sample responses:</p>
<ul>
      <li>5: The 5-frame is full so there are 5.</li>
      <li>6: There is 1 more than the last time.</li>
      <li>6: There are 6 fingers.</li>
    </ul>
  </solution>


