  <paragraphs>
    <title><custom ref="narrative-actividad-titulo"/></title>
    <p>[+++++++++++++++]</p>
    <p>The purpose of this How Many Do You See is for students to subitize or use grouping strategies to describe the images they see. When students use the structure of fingers and 5-frames to recognize and describe quantities they look for and make use of structure (MP7).</p>
  </paragraphs>

  <!-- Materiales requeridos de la actividad -->
  <paragraphs>
    <title><custom ref="materials-actividad-titulo"/></title>
    <p>[@@@@@@@@@@@@@@]</p>
    <!-- <xi:include href="./warm-RRRRRR-SSSSSS-mat.ptx"/>  -->
